# ── For the GitHub Issues contact form ──

# Create a fine-grained Personal Access Token at:
#   https://github.com/settings/tokens?type=beta
# Repository access: "Only select repositories" → pick this repo
# Permissions: Issues → "Read and write"
# Copy the token and add it as a repo secret named CONTACT_PAT

# For local development, copy this to .env (no quotes needed):
# VITE_GITHUB_PAT=github_pat_...
# VITE_GITHUB_REPO=Pradyu12/InfoSecure
